    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are in the oven, chop your <strong>smoked streaky</strong> <strong>bacon</strong> in half</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and <strong>chopped bacon</strong> to a separate baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the bacon is crispy</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
