    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken and bacon are cooking, slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper, then tear off 2 <strong>outer leaves</strong> per person and chop them in half</p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into wedges</p>",
