    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard </strong>(not a mustard fan? Go easy!) with your <strong>mayo</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>mustard mayo</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
