    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are golden, sprinkle the <strong>grated cheese</strong> over the top and return to the oven for 2-3 min or until the cheese has melted</p><p>Once done, drizzle the <strong>cheesy chips</strong> with most of your <strong>truffle oil</strong> (save some for dipping) – these are your <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>truffle chips</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
