        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with some <strong>mustard mayo</strong>, <strong>halved lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato</strong>, <strong>pulled chicken</strong>, <strong>smashed avocado</strong> and <strong>crispy bacon</strong> – this is your <strong>chicken & bacon club sandwich</strong></p><p>Using a serrated knife, slice the sandwich in half into triangles then <strong>skewer</strong> together</p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken & bacon club sandwich</strong> with the <strong>cheesy truffle chips</strong>, <strong>lettuce wedges</strong> and<strong> remaining truffle oil</strong> to the side for dipping and enjoy!</p>",
